    isnt possible.]</i></font>
    <p>Hmm, I was hoping that that recipe had been put in, but it evidently
    wasnt. Ill send a note to the game designer responsible for poison to take a
    look.
    <p>&nbsp;</p>
  <li><a href="http://boards.station.sony.com/everquest/Forum4/HTML/060002.html"><b>Falling
    Through the World</b></a><br>
    <font color="#072876"><i>[Quote from original post: I was at my friends
    house about logging onto my user, i was camped out in The Overthere, I coem
    in (screen is a picture of Qeynos) YOU have fallen or whatever YOU are hit
    by non-melee for 510 damage! At which point i was almost dead, then 2 liens
    of someone attacking and killing a stoneleer ****atrice, and I camped, what
    happened? When i get back to my comp i better not be under the world, and
